---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy — Practicing Presence"
  description="Privacy information for the Practicing Presence app and the practicingpresence.app website. No account, no sign-up, no ads, no tracking on this site."
  path="/privacy/"
>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container privacy">
      <h1>Privacy</h1>
      <p class="section__lead">
        Practicing Presence was built to be quiet — in every sense. Here is
        plainly what that means for your privacy.
      </p>

      <h2>This website (practicingpresence.app)</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>This is a static informational site. It has no user accounts and no forms.</li>
        <li>It sets no cookies and runs no advertising or third-party tracking scripts.</li>
        <li>
          Tutorial videos are embedded from YouTube in privacy-enhanced mode
          (youtube-nocookie.com). YouTube receives no cookie data from your visit
          unless you press play; if you do, YouTube&rsquo;s own&#32;
          <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" rel="noopener">privacy policy</a> applies.
        </li>
        <li>
          Links to the App Store, Google Play, Amazon, and affiliated sites take
          you to services governed by their own privacy policies.
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2>The Practicing Presence app</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>The app is 100% free, with no advertisements and no in-app purchases.</li>
        <li>No account or sign-up is required, and the app never asks for your name, email, or any personal profile.</li>
        <li>Your notification preferences (reminder start and end times) are stored on your device.</li>
        <li>
          Like most apps, it may use standard, anonymized crash and diagnostic
          reporting so problems can be found and fixed. For the authoritative,
          current data-practice disclosures, see the app&rsquo;s&#32;
          <a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/practicing-presence/id1467007716" rel="noopener">App Store listing</a>&#32;
          and&#32;
          <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.zeek.practicingpresence" rel="noopener">Google Play listing</a>.
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Practicing Presence and practicingpresence.app are maintained by B:Drive
        Communications, LLC. Questions about privacy or the app are welcome
        through the support links on the&#32;
        <a href="https://www.choosingpresence.org/christian-mindfulness-app" rel="noopener">Choosing Presence app page</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .privacy {
    max-width: 46rem;
  }

  .privacy h2 {
    margin-top: 2.25rem;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
  }

  .privacy ul {
    padding-left: 1.2rem;
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }
</style>
